frameDefinitions: An implicit cognizer judges that a particular State_of_affairs for which a Protagonist is responsible is socially unacceptable.
An Importer receives Goods from an Exporting_area, across a boundary or border to a different area, the Importing_area.
An Agent matches location with an Entity in order to fulfill some  Purpose.
frameExamples: He called it a <t>disgraceful</t> situation. INI
The U.S. <t>imported</t> some wheat in the period, although it exported about ten times as much.
I ca n't remember how many times he <t>visited</t> ! DNI
listRoleDefinitions: The entity or event which brings disgrace upon the <fen>Protagonist</fen>.
The person or organization responsible for the occurrence of the <fen>State_of_affairs</fen>.
The conscious entity, generally a person, that brings the <fen>Goods</fen> into the <fen>Importing_area</fen>.
The items of value whose location is changing.
The role <fen>Importing_area</fen> is the place that the <fen>Goods</fen> end up as a result of motion.
The place where the <fen>Goods</fen> are initially, before the being moved.
This role identifies the time when the <fen>Importer</fen> moves the <fen>Goods</fen>.
The sentient entity that is temporarily with the <fen>Entity</fen> in order to fulfil some <fen>Purpose</fen>.

The physical entity that is permanently associated with entities or characteristics that the <fen>Agent</fen> wishes to use for some <fen>Purpose</fen>.  During the visit, the <fen>Agent</fen> matches location with the <fen>Entity</fen>.
The time at which a visit is made.
A description of the position of the <fen>Agent</fen> during the visit.
listRoleExamples: You will soon learn the penalty for your disgraceful <fex>conduct</fex>.
It is disgraceful <fex>to our Public Works Department</fex>.
